about.summary: Helpful functions for using the properties of the Kronecker product, also has a memory efficient dot product.

name: kronprod
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "kronprod" %}
{% set version = "1.0.4" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
    url: https://github.com/Jbwasse2/{{ name }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: 2fefedf5d3077a88a77aeb237d7b0ef3c1e91b645ecbe92db5047a5fddd1e10c 

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.4
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.4
    - numpy
    - scipy

test:
  imports:
    - kronprod

about:
  home: https://github.com/Jbwasse2/kronprod 
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Helpful functions for using the properties of the Kronecker product, also has a memory efficient dot product.'

  dev_url: https://github.com/Jbwasse2/kronprod

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - Jbwasse2
